column2: SELECT u.up_col0 as [col0], # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + # as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, p.fiberMag_u, p.fiberMag_g, p.fiberMag_r, p.fiberMag_i, p.fiberMag_z, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMag_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER by x.up_id
